Use one of the following options to obtain a cluster for the training

- minikube
- docker desktop
- provided workshop cluster
- cloud cluster

Minikube setup with docker or VirtualBox:

* https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
* https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/start/


Start minikube

$ minikube start --cpus 2 --memory 4096
or
$ minikube start --cpus 2 --memory 4096 --ports 80:80 --driver docker


Setup kubectl 

* https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/tools/
